casebody.data:
Tony PATTERSON, Warden, et al., petitioners,
v.
Ricky ADKINS. No. 13-85. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 7, 2013.

Case below, 710 F.3d 1241 .

Motion of respondent for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit denied.
